  <!-- Posibles errores -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="errores-cool-titulo"/></title><p>[++++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Students select choices that indicate they are mixing up the parts of the graph that represent the lengths of the objects and the number of objects (as in options C or E).</p>
