    <title><custom ref="apoyo-cool-titulo"/></title><p>[++++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Before the next day’s warm-up have students discuss what the x's on a line plot represent and what the numbers along the bottom of the line plot represent.</p>
  </paragraphs>

</postlude>

</project>